  "title": "Occupational Therapist | Nursing Home",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Conduct initial evaluations to determine care needs for elderly admissions</li>\n  <li>Implement regular care plan reviews with appropriate therapeutic interventions</li>\n  <li>Develop and facilitate group therapy programs tailored for elderly participants</li>\n  <li>Collaborate in multidisciplinary team meetings for integrated care planning</li>\n  <li>Plan and execute group therapy programme and activities for elderly</li>\n  <li>Develop occupational therapy interventions for clients with Dementia, Psychiatric illness, Musculoskeletal and Neurological conditions</li>\n  <li>Evaluate and optimize therapy schedules with complete documentation</li>\n  <li>Have knowledge of dementia issues and able to manage elderlywho display behavioral problems.</li>\n  <li>Establish supportive relationships with their families and caregivers</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements and Qualifications:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor degree / Diploma in Occupational Therapy</li>\n  <li>Full registeration with APHC</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years of working experience with disability patient</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Check out Aber Care Website for more details</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested applicants please email your detailed resume to career@abercare.sg</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Abercare.sg | EA License No. 18C9070 | KOH SU WEN, CLARISSA| Registration No. R24119504|</p>",
